[SN]TITLE[SN]
What do you want to know about university?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
We asked you to send in your questions on the topic of university education for BBC Education correspondent Sean Coughlan to investigate.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
We picked out four questions. Now it's over to you to choose which one you most want answered:
Where will I see Sean's answer?
Sean's story answering the question will be published on the BBC News website and will appear on this page and the Education Section of the site site as well as our Facebook page.
Why are we doing this?
We want to write stories which matter to you.
You can send us your questions about whatever interests you and BBC News will try to answer them.
Other questions you've wanted us to answer
If you are reading this page on the BBC News app, you will need to visit the mobile version of the BBC website to submit your question.
